Defendant in custody at Dodge Correctional, appearing by zoom.
NO CONTEST plea entered to count 2, 4th degree sexual assault as repeater.  Convicted.
The State moves to dismiss and read in count 1.  Motion granted.
Sentence Withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for two (2) years, consecutive to the prison sentences presently being served on Ozaukee County case no: 22 CF 140 and Manitowoc County case no: 19 CF 457, to commence upon defendant's discharge date after extended supervision ends.
Conditions of probation:
1)	Pay court costs;
2)	pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
3)	provide DNA sample;
4)	undergo a psycho-sexual evaluation and follow through;
5)	have no contact with A.R.;
6)	maintain absolute sobriety;
7)	spend sixty (60) days in the county jail, under the Huber Law, stayed and to be imposed at the agent's discretion and upon order of the court;
8)	AODA assessment and follow through;
9)	Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
10)	Submit to random urine screens and pay for same.
Minutes.
